### MongoDB Calls Endpoints
# These endpoints provide paginated access to calls with various filters

# --- Variables ---
@host = http://localhost:8000
@api_key = your_api_key_here
@auth_token = Bearer {{api_key}}

### Get Recent Calls (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/recent?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Recent Calls (Page 2)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/recent?page=2
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Oldest Calls (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/oldest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Successful Calls (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/successful?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Failed Calls (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/failed?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Longest Calls (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/longest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Shortest Calls (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/shortest?page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Calls by Source (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/by-source?source=webform&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Calls by Source - Phone (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/by-source?source=phone&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Calls by Source - Email (Page 1)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/by-source?source=email&page=1
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Get Call by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/call_id_here
Authorization: {{auth_token}}

### Sample Call ID lookup
GET {{host}}/api/v1/mongo/calls/67890abcdef1234567890abc
Authorization: {{auth_token}}
